Functionalities, modules, actors of the system

User types/roles:
	- admin
	- evaluator
	- professor
	- student

Application modules:
	- real-time monitoring/course for each course
	- light:
		- light sensor
		- shutter controller
		- lighting controller
	- temperatur:
		- temperature sensor		
		- heating controller
		- air conditioning
	- TODO: 
		- air composition analyser (oxygen, CO2 etc)
	- social:
		- questionnaire handling (web)app
		- real-time feedback display

Actors:
	- Admin: 
		- start system
		- stop system
		- add user
		- remove user
		- edit user
		- 
	- Evaluator:
		- generate report
	- Professor:
		- 
		- monitor real-time feedback of students
	- Student:
		- answer questionnaires